      • withLoginTokenSource

        public CognitoCredentialsProvider.CognitoCredentialsProviderBuilder withLoginTokenSource​(CognitoLoginTokenSource loginTokenSource)
        Sets a login token source for the credentials provider. The login token source will be used to gather additional login tokens to submit as part of the HTTP request sent to Cognito. A login token source allows you to dynamically add login tokens on a per-request basis. Using a login token source requires you to follow certain requirements in order to avoid undesirable behavior. See the documentation for `CognitoLoginTokenSource` for further details.
        Parameters:
        loginTokenSource - object to source login tokens from before every HTTP request to Cognito
        Returns:
        The current builder
